00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:45.300
Google displays a similar graph online,

00:01:45.400 --> 00:01:47.900
when you go to search up whether a place is busy or not.

00:01:48.800 --> 00:01:51.000
Data is a big part of our daily lives.

00:01:51.100 --> 00:01:54.200
In the next two videos, you will see animations that explain

00:01:54.300 --> 00:01:56.900
